New to Consulting? Firstly, thanks for choosing Consulting! We hope you enjoy using it as much as we enjoy developing it. To help get you started we've made it super easy for you to create a site exactly the same (well pretty much) as the demo in no time at all.

Below you'll see the Run Installer button. To install the demo data simply hit this button and watch your site come to life. Just a few points to note:

  1. Make sure that the Page Builder and Contact Form 7 plugins are installed and activated before running.
  2. The installation should only be run once and it should be on a fresh installation of WordPress.
  3. Once the installation completes you'll see a notification message.
  4. Do not refresh the page until installation is complete (might take a few minutes).
  5. When complete make sure you check all the links on your site. Update these if needed from Appearance -> Menus.
  6. All of the demo images will be replaced with a grey placeholder image.

If you run into problems or have any questions at all just send us a support ticket from the members area and we'll be on hand to help. You can submit a support ticket here.

Enjoy using Consulting!
